f6_assessments.q2:
The proposal could improve the way it structures its milestones so that progress is auditable. 

From my understanding of the proposal, there are at least three milestones in this project. 
a. Hiring and onboarding of educator with needed language to reach South African audience;
b. Creation of Tiktok channel;
c. Conduct of education sessions

To improve letter B and C, it would be good to have a better grasp of how many they are targeting to reach and how they plan to build an audience.
